  "text": "High aspect ratio microneedles have been previously reported as a suitable platform for cell transfection with high efficiencies [CITATION_1] 35 , but offering limited transfection control by their mechanical, passive delivery mechanism. Moreover, such systems are not cell specific, making them impractical for heterogeneous cell cultures.",
